ygData.subject: Re: Plane of losses
ygData.msgSnippet: Heh I wouldn t say feared because if it s not hopeless most people aren t going to fear the zone. Naeeldar ... From: Kimes, Dean W.
ygData.messageBody:
Heh I wouldn't say feared because if it's not hopeless most people aren't
going to fear the zone.

Naeeldar
